       Planet Strike is similar in most aspects to Aliens of Gold.
       However, a number of new features, both cosmetic and active, have
       been added. These are listed below.

       1)  1 episode: 20 regular floors (0-19), 4 bonus floors (20-23)
       2)  No elevators are used; just transporters
       3)  New uniforms and language for all actors
       4)  Some new Aliens
