       6)  Morphing capability for some actors
       7)  Automap zoom to help locate pushwalls
       8)  Fewer access key cards
       9)  Ability to activate guards before Blake gets to them
       10) Invisibility cloaks for guards and aliens
       11) Switches, Doors, and Guards activated when guards/aliens killed
       12) Easier to enable Debug Mode
